### [/planets/{{planetId}}] - Update one planet field(s)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/planets/{{planetId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"favoriteColor": "Crimson"
}



### [/planets/{{planetId}}] - Delete one planet
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/planets/{{planetId}}

